  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To determine if adding Escitalopram to current mood stabilizer (MS) or atypical antipsychotic
      (AA) will improve in rates similar to or better than adding a placebo (inactive pill)in
      resistant bipolar patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Terminated</overall_status>
  <why_stopped>
